            <h2>Gameplay</h2>

            <p>
                The Blacksmith is a Life you can choose in the game Fantasy Life. It is one of 14 Lives that can be
                chosen at any time during the game by visiting the Guild Master (except during a story mission).

                The Blacksmith uses hammers to craft weapons, armour and tools. There are 139 blacksmith recipes in the
                base
                game and 233 with the DLC
            </p>

            <h2>Skills</h2>

            <p>
                When the player chooses the Blacksmith life, they learn 4 skills: Smithing, Weaponsmithing, Armoursmithing, and Metal Tool Smithing. The max skill level is 15 (20 with the DLC). To unlock the new cap, you must reach Legend rank and talk to Divinus with the Blacksmith Life activated. He will increase the cap of all 4 skills to 20 and upgrade the licence to God-in-Training rank.
            </p>

